<HEADLINE>
<P>
REGIONAL EARNINGS: MATTHEWS EXPECTS TO SEE TRIPLING OF EARNINGS 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
Matthews Studio Equipment Group in Burbank said it expects to report that its 
earnings tripled and revenues rose by more than 50% in the fiscal year ending 
Sept. 30, compared to fiscal 1989. 
</P>
<P>
For the year that ended Sept. 30, 1989, Matthews earned $138,000 on $14.7 
million in revenues. 
</P>
<P>
Matthews, which makes and rents film and television production equipment, said 
the expected improvement in its financial results is due to the growth of its 
rental business. 
</P>
</TEXT>
