Chancellor's Back: John Chancellor, commentator for "NBC Nightly News," has 
recovered from heart surgery and will return to the program Wednesday, NBC 
announced Monday. Chancellor, 62, who underwent double-bypass surgery in late 
June, will make weekly appearances through September, an NBC spokeswoman said. 
