IRAQ -- FOREIGN RELATIONS -- KUWAIT; MILITARY CONFRONTATIONS; UNITED STATES -- 
ARMED FORCES -- PERSIAN GULF; UNITED STATES -- FOREIGN RELATIONS -- IRAQ; IRAQ 
-- ARMED FORCES -- KUWAIT 
</P>
