</P>
</DATE>
<SECTION>
<P>
Business; Part D; Page 2; Column 1; Financial Desk 
</P>
</SECTION>
<LENGTH>
<P>
55 words 
</P>
</LENGTH>
<HEADLINE>
<P>
BRIEFLY 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<BYLINE>
<P>
From Times Staff and Wire Reports 
</P>
</BYLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
Number of Oil, Gas Drilling Rigs Up 27: The rise in the number of working oil 
and gas rigs in the United States, boosted the total to 1,039 this week -- an 
indication that the domestic Oil Patch finally is feeling the effects of the 
Middle East crisis, Baker Hughes Inc. reported. A year ago this week, the count 
totaled 950. 
</P>
