<P>
Column 
</P>
</TYPE>
</DOC>
<DOC>
<DOCNO> LA091190-0141 </DOCNO>
<DOCID> 274641 </DOCID>
<DATE>
<P>
September 11, 1990, Tuesday, Orange County Edition 
</P>
</DATE>
<SECTION>
<P>
Sports; Part C; Page 13; Column 2; Sports Desk 
</P>
</SECTION>
<LENGTH>
<P>
284 words 
</P>
